    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** Above, we needed the constraint [Set < i].  But one can use propositional resizing again to make [imp_Trm] land in the lowest universe, if that is needed.  (We'll in fact let it land in any universe [u].)  To do this, we need to assume [Funext] in the definition of the truncation itself. *)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
