    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  (** [Funext] implies that [Trm A] is a proposition, so [PropResizing] can be used to put it in any universe. The construction passes through universe [k], which represents [max(i,Set+1)]. *)\n  "
    },
